====== WENOEXT library ======

The weighted essentially non-oscillatory library was initially developed by
Tobias Martin at the University of Rostock. The method and its validation has 
been demonstrated in

@Article{computation6010006,
AUTHOR = {Martin, Tobias and Shevchuk, Ivan},
TITLE = {Implementation and Validation of Semi-Implicit WENO Schemes Using OpenFOAM},
JOURNAL = {Computation},
VOLUME = {6},
YEAR = {2018},
NUMBER = {1},
ARTICLE NUMBER = {6}
}

Please make a proper reference to this open access paper if the library is used. 


